00:24:29.720 --> 00:24:32.279
My faith is saying my soulmate is in front of me,

00:24:32.280 --> 00:24:33.599
so hurry up and confess.

00:24:33.600 --> 00:24:35.519
You are so lucky.

00:24:35.520 --> 00:24:38.800
Why is my name Dahlia and not Husniya Radwa?

00:24:45.520 --> 00:24:46.360
Let's eat.

00:24:57.200 --> 00:24:58.799
Can I get something in the car?

00:24:58.800 --> 00:25:00.839
- One minute. - Okay.

00:25:00.840 --> 00:25:02.520
I promise, one minute.

00:25:08.600 --> 00:25:09.440
Hey, Niya.

00:25:10.280 --> 00:25:11.839
What are you doing here?

00:25:11.840 --> 00:25:14.079
Where's your rich boyfriend?

00:25:14.080 --> 00:25:16.159
Where does he work? Where's his house?

00:25:16.160 --> 00:25:18.039
Who's my rich boyfriend?

00:25:18.040 --> 00:25:20.119
That man who choked me the other day.

00:25:20.120 --> 00:25:22.319
I want to settle it with him.

00:25:22.320 --> 00:25:24.359
Are you crazy? Just go home.

00:25:24.360 --> 00:25:25.720
Hey, Niya.

00:25:27.000 --> 00:25:29.039
- Hey, Niya. - Let me go.

00:25:29.040 --> 00:25:30.919
Why are you so arrogant?

00:25:30.920 --> 00:25:32.719
Are you still upset because I left you?

00:25:32.720 --> 00:25:34.759
Hey. Come on, Syafiq.

00:25:34.760 --> 00:25:37.959
I was actually thankful when you left me

00:25:37.960 --> 00:25:40.559
because I'd never liked you.

00:25:40.560 --> 00:25:43.439
I was with you because I was sorry for you.

00:25:43.440 --> 00:25:45.719
I couldn't see you cry and commit suicide

00:25:45.720 --> 00:25:47.840
because I rejected you.

00:25:50.280 --> 00:25:54.000
So, what will you do if I don't do anything you say?

00:25:55.080 --> 00:25:57.439
Threaten me by saying you'll jump again?

00:25:57.440 --> 00:26:01.200
You want to cry so everyone can hear and see it?

00:26:01.880 --> 00:26:03.119
- Sissy. - You...

00:26:03.120 --> 00:26:05.439
What? You want to slap me?

00:26:05.440 --> 00:26:06.839
Slap me.

00:26:06.840 --> 00:26:09.040
Go on. Hurry up. I'm hungry.

00:26:20.280 --> 00:26:22.600
Where's the ring box?

00:26:31.040 --> 00:26:35.240
If you slap me, the thing between Ridz and you are done. Got it?

00:26:37.360 --> 00:26:39.280
Ridz made that for me, idiot!

00:26:49.720 --> 00:26:50.960
Ridz.

00:26:51.960 --> 00:26:54.879
She's a woman, idiot!

00:26:54.880 --> 00:26:56.599
Ridz! Ridz, that's enough.

00:26:56.600 --> 00:26:58.319
Step away!

00:26:58.320 --> 00:27:00.319
Ridz!

00:27:00.320 --> 00:27:02.600
Stop! Stop!

00:27:04.920 --> 00:27:06.040
Ridz.

00:27:19.640 --> 00:27:23.880
As the person responsible for taking care of the company,

00:27:24.960 --> 00:27:26.680
I'm left with no choice, Husniya.

00:27:27.680 --> 00:27:31.640
Pack up your things and get out of here.

00:27:34.680 --> 00:27:35.680
Responsible?

00:27:36.360 --> 00:27:40.200
My boss, Syawal Azizan, is talking about responsibility?

00:27:40.840 --> 00:27:43.359
I've worked here for more than seven years.

00:27:43.360 --> 00:27:45.120
I've never had any problems.

00:27:45.960 --> 00:27:49.480
This is my second issue and you want to fire me?

00:27:50.440 --> 00:27:53.440
What about the times I saved your ass, boss?

00:27:54.440 --> 00:27:55.799
You are so lazy at work.

00:27:55.800 --> 00:27:57.999
Yet you claimed credit so quickly.

00:27:58.000 --> 00:27:59.800
What a nice boss.

00:28:00.320 --> 00:28:02.200
With all the accusations

00:28:02.800 --> 00:28:05.280
you've made against me,

00:28:06.080 --> 00:28:07.639
I'm making this official.

00:28:07.640 --> 00:28:09.360
Husniya Radwa,

00:28:10.160 --> 00:28:11.039
you are fired!

00:28:11.040 --> 00:28:12.400
Get out!

00:28:20.560 --> 00:28:22.519
I know what I did was wrong,

00:28:22.520 --> 00:28:25.119
but I can't let anyone hurt you, Radwa.

00:28:25.120 --> 00:28:26.040
You!

00:28:27.360 --> 00:28:29.240
You are the reason I'm hurting.

00:28:30.760 --> 00:28:32.719
If you hadn't taken me away

00:28:32.720 --> 00:28:35.839
when I was forced to marry Adib, my mom wouldn't have come here

00:28:35.840 --> 00:28:39.800
and gotten angry that I got a final warning.

00:28:42.320 --> 00:28:43.159
Adib.

00:28:43.160 --> 00:28:46.599
He wouldn't be asking for 50,000 in compensation.

00:28:46.600 --> 00:28:50.439
If it wasn't because of that, I'd never go to that silly reunion

00:28:50.440 --> 00:28:51.959
to win the lucky draw.

00:28:51.960 --> 00:28:55.039
Syafiq wouldn't come here to look for you because he was upset with you.

00:28:55.040 --> 00:28:58.960
You wouldn't beat him up and I wouldn't be fired.

00:29:01.880 --> 00:29:04.639
I told you that I really hate you.

00:29:04.640 --> 00:29:08.839
I have told you so many times why I didn't want to see you,

00:29:08.840 --> 00:29:11.440
but you still come to me.

00:29:13.560 --> 00:29:16.800
When will you get it through your head

00:29:17.400 --> 00:29:20.320
that you're the reason behind my pain?

00:29:22.720 --> 00:29:24.799
Till I die?

00:29:24.800 --> 00:29:28.520
Will you wait for me to die before you stop hurting me?

00:29:29.920 --> 00:29:31.080
Is that it?

00:29:37.600 --> 00:29:39.080
That's enough, Ridz.

00:29:39.960 --> 00:29:40.800
Enough.

00:30:04.000 --> 00:30:04.880
Niya.

00:30:05.920 --> 00:30:08.039
Breathe, Niya. Breathe.

00:30:08.040 --> 00:30:10.999
- Follow me. You need to breathe. - No.

00:30:11.000 --> 00:30:14.120
- Follow me. - No!

00:30:16.680 --> 00:30:17.560
Niya.

00:30:18.600 --> 00:30:21.919
Niya. Niya, wake up, please.

00:30:21.920 --> 00:30:23.080
Niya.

00:30:28.720 --> 00:30:30.479
Peace be upon you, Radwa.

00:30:30.480 --> 00:30:32.439
Peace be upon you too.

00:30:32.440 --> 00:30:33.640
Dad.

00:30:34.760 --> 00:30:36.280
How are you today, Radwa?

00:30:38.040 --> 00:30:39.800
I brought some fruits.

00:30:41.080 --> 00:30:43.160
Come, let me feed you.

00:30:53.520 --> 00:30:55.000
- Dad. - Yes.

00:30:55.840 --> 00:30:58.280
I'll give you your allowance for this month a bit late.

00:30:58.880 --> 00:31:02.960
- I was fired. - It's okay. I know.

00:31:04.760 --> 00:31:06.919
I promise I'll find another job quickly.

00:31:06.920 --> 00:31:09.160
Please don't worry about the allowance, Dad.

00:31:11.240 --> 00:31:12.800
It's okay.

00:31:15.040 --> 00:31:16.960
Would you like to work in a hotel

00:31:17.840 --> 00:31:19.560
as a senior manager?

00:31:20.400 --> 00:31:24.160
You'll earn slightly more than you do now.

00:31:25.480 --> 00:31:27.479
After you get discharged,

00:31:27.480 --> 00:31:29.160
you can start working.

00:31:29.760 --> 00:31:33.840
No interviews. No scanning. I can suddenly start work?

00:31:34.600 --> 00:31:36.000
Who offered me the job, Dad?

00:31:37.160 --> 00:31:38.919
It's not important, Radwa.

00:31:38.920 --> 00:31:40.800
It is for me.

00:31:43.000 --> 00:31:45.040
Just listen to me, Radwa.

00:31:45.640 --> 00:31:47.680
Come on, let's eat.

00:31:49.400 --> 00:31:52.920
If you refuse to tell me, I won't eat.

00:31:59.320 --> 00:32:00.640
Actually,

00:32:01.800 --> 00:32:02.640
it was Ridz.

00:32:03.600 --> 00:32:06.039
- Ridz offered you this job. - Dad!

00:32:06.040 --> 00:32:09.480
Do you know he's the reason I'm here right now?

00:32:10.080 --> 00:32:12.439
If he hadn't taken me away before my marriage,

00:32:12.440 --> 00:32:14.279
none of this would've happen.

00:32:14.280 --> 00:32:16.279
This is all Ridz's fault.

00:32:16.280 --> 00:32:20.719
Radwa, please listen to me.

00:32:20.720 --> 00:32:23.720
It's not his fault. It's mine.

00:32:24.680 --> 00:32:29.680
I called him and asked him to take you away that day.

00:32:31.080 --> 00:32:32.439
It's my fault.

00:32:32.440 --> 00:32:34.040
Why, Dad?

00:32:35.200 --> 00:32:36.360
It's because...

00:32:37.840 --> 00:32:39.480
I want you to be happy, Radwa.

00:32:45.600 --> 00:32:49.280
Your happiness lies with Ridz, Radwa.

00:32:54.480 --> 00:32:55.320
Dad...

00:33:11.000 --> 00:33:13.400
I hate everyone

00:33:15.960 --> 00:33:19.760
because they treat me so badly.

00:33:38.880 --> 00:33:40.480
I came to save you.

00:33:42.560 --> 00:33:44.159
You think your grand gesture is cute?

00:33:44.160 --> 00:33:46.359
You might woo other women,

00:33:46.360 --> 00:33:49.479
but honestly, I don't think this is cute at all.

00:33:49.480 --> 00:33:51.880
No need to play a hero, cutting off the window bars.

00:33:53.040 --> 00:33:57.199
- And let you marry that dude? - It's far better than marrying you.

00:33:57.200 --> 00:34:00.999
- Are you mad at me? - Mad? I'm no longer upset.

00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:05.239
I just hate you, Ridz. I hate you with all my heart!

00:34:05.240 --> 00:34:08.719
You're the reason I hated myself.

00:34:09.320 --> 00:34:11.040
I get that you hate me.

00:34:12.639 --> 00:34:14.119
Thank you for your understanding.

00:34:14.120 --> 00:34:16.039
Now, get lost!

00:34:16.040 --> 00:34:19.198
You are the reason I'm hurting.

00:34:19.199 --> 00:34:22.039
I never meant to hurt you, Radwa.

00:34:22.040 --> 00:34:24.159
As long as you're around,

00:34:25.920 --> 00:34:28.840
I keep hurting.

00:34:31.880 --> 00:34:34.400
When will you get it through your head

00:34:35.760 --> 00:34:38.840
that you're the reason behind my pain?

00:34:41.040 --> 00:34:43.119
Till I die?

00:34:43.120 --> 00:34:46.840
Will you wait for me to die before you stop hurting me?

00:34:48.280 --> 00:34:49.960
Is that it?

00:35:23.960 --> 00:35:26.520
You're so kind to me, Ridz,

00:35:28.400 --> 00:35:32.800
but I'm still not kind to you.

00:36:42.240 --> 00:36:45.119
Because he hasn't called me...

00:36:45.120 --> 00:36:46.240
Call you what?

00:36:47.560 --> 00:36:48.600
Treasure.

00:36:55.000 --> 00:36:58.040
Ridz, please pick up.

00:37:14.640 --> 00:37:17.480
If I don't pick up,

00:37:19.240 --> 00:37:20.520
I've already died.

00:37:37.920 --> 00:37:39.280
<i>That's enough, Ridz.</i>

00:37:40.320 --> 00:37:41.400
<i>Enough.</i>

00:38:19.280 --> 00:38:21.960
- Peace be upon you. - Peace be upon you too.

00:38:22.960 --> 00:38:24.159
Can I help you?

00:38:24.160 --> 00:38:28.040
I'm here to see Mr. Thariq Ridzuwan.

00:38:28.800 --> 00:38:30.040
Isn't that Radwa?

00:38:34.120 --> 00:38:35.560
Go and see her.

00:38:37.760 --> 00:38:41.560
<i>Will you wait for me to die before you stop hurting me?</i>

00:38:42.720 --> 00:38:43.560
Come on.

00:38:44.840 --> 00:38:45.840
Let's go.

00:38:49.160 --> 00:38:50.639
You came a bit late.

00:38:50.640 --> 00:38:51.560
There he goes.

00:39:11.520 --> 00:39:16.120
{\an8}FIFTY THOUSAND RINGGIT ONLY.

00:39:21.640 --> 00:39:22.680
What is this?

00:39:23.520 --> 00:39:26.160
Sorry, I didn't tell you the other day.

00:39:27.640 --> 00:39:28.720
Tell me what?

00:39:42.240 --> 00:39:44.959
Stop disturbing Radwa.

00:39:44.960 --> 00:39:47.160
Don't tell her I paid for this.

00:39:49.080 --> 00:39:51.520
Tell her that you don't want compensation.

00:39:54.360 --> 00:39:55.640
I really...

00:39:57.320 --> 00:39:58.960
care about her.

00:40:01.400 --> 00:40:03.000
Even though she hates me.

00:40:05.800 --> 00:40:07.640
I will not hurt her.

00:40:09.080 --> 00:40:10.680
I will not cause her trouble.

00:40:12.720 --> 00:40:14.280
Can you do the same?

00:40:16.960 --> 00:40:18.160
Do you understand me now?

00:40:20.040 --> 00:40:21.119
Yes, sir.

00:40:21.120 --> 00:40:23.720
- Do you understand me? - Yes, sir!

00:40:40.640 --> 00:40:41.880
Actually,

00:40:43.160 --> 00:40:45.399
I really like you, Husniya.

00:40:45.400 --> 00:40:47.320
Even though I know that...

00:40:48.880 --> 00:40:50.080
you don't like me.

00:40:52.880 --> 00:40:54.040
Thank you.

00:40:56.200 --> 00:40:57.320
Husniya.

00:40:58.680 --> 00:41:01.520
There's something you need to know.

00:41:07.080 --> 00:41:08.000
Mom.

00:41:09.000 --> 00:41:10.000
Mom!

00:41:10.520 --> 00:41:11.360
Wa.

00:41:12.240 --> 00:41:15.120
Did you force Adib to pay the 50,000 ringgit?

00:41:15.960 --> 00:41:18.599
Radwa, my beloved daughter,

00:41:18.600 --> 00:41:23.479
I have been waiting for you to come home for some time now.

00:41:23.480 --> 00:41:26.319
I have been mentioning your name.

00:41:26.320 --> 00:41:30.240
Today, I want to introduce you to someone.

00:41:33.560 --> 00:41:34.919
Okay, this is Zafir.

00:41:34.920 --> 00:41:37.200
He just came back from the States.

00:41:38.800 --> 00:41:43.440
Soon, you two will get engaged.

00:41:45.360 --> 00:41:47.120
Hi, Husniya. How are you?

00:41:58.680 --> 00:42:01.039
This is all Ridz's fault.

00:42:01.040 --> 00:42:03.760
It's not his fault. It's mine.

00:42:13.080 --> 00:42:14.800
Ridz, pick up, please.

00:42:22.960 --> 00:42:23.800
Ridz.

00:42:25.600 --> 00:42:26.920
I'm sorry

00:42:28.240 --> 00:42:29.960
for always blaming you.

00:42:33.480 --> 00:42:36.599
It would be the same even if I married Adib.

00:42:36.600 --> 00:42:40.160
Mom will always find a way to make sure I suffer.

00:42:42.080 --> 00:42:43.480
It's like selling her child.

00:42:44.080 --> 00:42:45.600
She doesn't care about me.

00:42:47.120 --> 00:42:49.040
My siblings hate me.

00:42:51.520 --> 00:42:53.320
My classmates bully me.

00:42:55.280 --> 00:42:59.880
My boss hates me, even though it's not my fault, Ridz.

00:43:01.760 --> 00:43:05.000
It's not your fault either. Not at all.

00:43:06.240 --> 00:43:07.639
It's all my fault.

00:43:07.640 --> 00:43:10.480
It's my fault for being born into this world!

00:43:14.000 --> 00:43:15.919
I'm tired, Ridz.

00:43:15.920 --> 00:43:17.880
My head feels like...

00:43:19.080 --> 00:43:20.439
There's so much going on.

00:43:20.440 --> 00:43:22.920
I have anxiety and depression.

00:43:23.520 --> 00:43:25.399
I have trauma. What do I not have?

00:43:25.400 --> 00:43:27.919
I have everything. I feel so suffocated.

00:43:27.920 --> 00:43:30.040
I'm suffocated. I feel suffocated.

00:43:32.080 --> 00:43:32.920
Ridz.

00:43:37.360 --> 00:43:39.080
I'm such a loser.

00:43:40.080 --> 00:43:41.240
I'm worthless.

00:43:44.640 --> 00:43:46.200
I'm useless.

00:43:53.200 --> 00:43:54.320
Husniya Radwa.

00:43:58.120 --> 00:44:00.280
You are priceless to me.

00:44:05.040 --> 00:44:05.880
Will you...

00:44:09.080 --> 00:44:10.280
Will you marry me,

00:44:11.720 --> 00:44:12.880
my treasure?

00:44:16.120 --> 00:44:20.080
{\an8}TO BE CONTINUED

00:44:27.560 --> 00:44:31.119
{\an8}The Prophet said we should choose a wife based on four criteria.

00:44:31.120 --> 00:44:34.679
{\an8}Faith, beauty, wealth, and lineage.

00:44:34.680 --> 00:44:35.920
{\an8}I'm pretty.

00:44:36.760 --> 00:44:37.799
{\an8}Radwa is pretty.

00:44:37.800 --> 00:44:40.039
{\an8}If you bring him home,

00:44:40.040 --> 00:44:42.159
{\an8}you don't have to get engaged to Zafir.

00:44:42.160 --> 00:44:46.759
{\an8}We are lawyers representing Ms. Husniya Radwa.

00:44:46.760 --> 00:44:48.519
{\an8}Wow, she must be rich.

00:44:48.520 --> 00:44:50.639
{\an8}Why couldn't she afford it?

00:44:50.640 --> 00:44:52.119
{\an8}Come on, it's Radwa.

00:44:52.120 --> 00:44:56.959
{\an8}Let me take care of you. Let me love you every moment of the day.

00:44:56.960 --> 00:44:58.640
{\an8}So please.

00:44:59.960 --> 00:45:01.519
{\an8}What are you doing?

00:45:01.520 --> 00:45:04.240
{\an8}NEXT EPISODE PREVIEW

